    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition, truly a rare find that looks and drives like it just left the factory. The exterior paint is flawless with no chips or scratches, maintaining a showroom shine, while the interior remains pristine with no signs of wear on the upholstery or dashboard. Mechanically, the car is perfect, having been meticulously maintained with a full service history and all original components in top working order. This is a collector-quality example that will satisfy even the most discerning buyer looking for a turn-key, as-new experience.",
