    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable, budget-friendly option for those who prioritize utility over perfection. The engine and transmission are functional, though the car shows noticeable cosmetic wear both inside and out, including some scuffs and upholstery aging. It has been used regularly and would benefit from some minor maintenance to bring it up to its best potential. This is an honest, high-mileage driver that gets the job done without the premium price tag.",
      "price": 19500.0,
